Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:51.08,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,225)}Yawn Master
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's probably not a bad match,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's too soon for me to be looking at arranged marriages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How old do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? It's not as if you're going to be young forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not often that you get matches as nice as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:15.65,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fnFormal 436 BT\bord0\c&H252523&\frz293.584\pos(392.36,767.25)}From Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but I'm only going to meet him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll give them a call too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.67,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fnFormal 436 BT\bord0\c&H252523&\frz293.584\pos(392.36,767.25)}From Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if I'll be young forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! I'm still young!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.55,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.125\fs108\bord0\b1\fnPapyrus\pos(1162.921,184.5)\c&HDAD7D1&}Copy it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I can't believe how sleepy I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, you were completely asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it can't be helped with this kind of weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For real, the weather sure is nice today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sittin' out here in the sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like I'm bundled up in a nice, fluffy blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was just such a magnificent yawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take my eyes off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Très bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the very picture of a yawn! I've never seen a yawn like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you've come from the land of yawns to spread yawning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, yawn master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess all people have at least one redeeming trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, teach me how to yawn like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the yawn training hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't quite the same somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me join in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:47.11,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(277,228)}Vaguely Youth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Afternoon classes have started already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's your fault, Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping on the roof?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Because the sky was just so blue, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.13,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,646)\bord2.25\b1\fs76.5\c&H6259BF&\pos(703.82,679.5)\frz26.918}Smack
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You three! Ten laps around the schoolyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! I can't believe those girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have entrance exams next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What are you so irritated about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some girls in your class were apparently practicing yawning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,during lunch, and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, practicing yawning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it, but I don't see much wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Being easygoing is one of the privileges of adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Privilege, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think you can still only take adolescence so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. You want to go flower gazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Flower gazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.14,Note,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs108\bord0\shad4.5\fad(0,562)\pos(705.843,333)\4c&H2F2E2C&}After School
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.48,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\c&HDBD6C7&\b1\fs117\3c&H563E2C&\pos(509.663,155.25)\frx14\fry34\frz339.874}Library
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, what happened was,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it turned out to be hashed beef instead of curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You can't even tell hashed beef and curry apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sometimes, I can't tell 'em apart even if I eat 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's having way too little sense of taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're in a position to say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're heading home, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When you leave, make sure to turn the lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it was this late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already getting dark outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Miss Kagura, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it sure makes you feel like we're living our youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Basic strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that for the swim team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to make it to the national level this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of gunning for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always thought the swim team was on break except for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think we're the same as you people in the Go-home Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-home Club? What's the Go-home Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the students who aren't in any clubs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and go home as soon as classes are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, people like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you guys at school this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because she said she needed to look for some book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all at the library together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was more like we were just chatting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are lucky, you have this freedom about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're barely getting passing grades and you think we have freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're freaking dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really not that funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:52.48,EpisodeTitle,,152,0,0,,{\fad(269,0)}Adults' Flower Gazing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's a nice looking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've dressed more properly if I'd known it was a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said we were going flower gazing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didn't I say we were going to a hotel bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Eiko, a section chief, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know how companies work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but isn't that a pretty big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose, but all I've gotten is more work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual work I do hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You reprimand your subordinates and get reprimanded by your supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my work does directly affects the results of operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess in that sense, it's work worth doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing! You seem so grownup, Eiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? You two are grownups too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We also have important jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,educating the promising youth of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally grownup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Miss Minamo, you're a P.E. Teacher, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any intention of switching jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A sports gym affiliated with our company
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is looking for a chief instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, you'd be treated as a full-time employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The place is high-class, so you'd undoubtedly double your salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Switching jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, if you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You brought it up so suddenly, it caught me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not going to switch jobs, because I love my current job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It never even occurred to me to even think about switching jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it, Eiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Nyamo, I'd have to walk to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my eraser...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, both Mother and Father are out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:22.50,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs81\fnCambria\3c&H28251B&\pos(1041.573,213.75)\frx338\fry328\frz332.458}Mihama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare me! No! No! I'm sorry! Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here alone at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran out of convenience stores, so I was headed to the eraser...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to a convenience store to buy an eraser, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never gone out alone this late at night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. I've heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They show up around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm out drinking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, do you two have anyone special right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any scandalous stories to tell about us lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We've got the right number of people too! Hurry on over, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I told the boys at work about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both pretty nice guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:56.14,EpisodeTitle,,152,0,0,,{\fad(242,0)}Children's Flower Gazing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like going flower gazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for treating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem. After all, you walked me to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't very well leave you alone when you looked at me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to the convenience store at night is such fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess once you're grownup,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you can even shop in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be so nice. I can't wait to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can't wait to grow up, huh, Chiyo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can, Miss Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd never really thought about it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about me going to work and getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to work and getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, it's a little hard to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in your case, you're still little,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't think that's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still can't wait to grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, good evening! I'm Nakku, aka Nakuro Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm Mitchy, aka Michiru Ogino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is Nakku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and Mitchy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thrilling Main Street of Youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But you know, Mitchy, did you see the cherry blossoms in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're sure blooming early this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Like the cherry trees in the park near the studio are in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll bet people who were planning on going flower gazing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}next week or the week after are pretty disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you don't change your plans and go soon, it's all going to be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I know. Cherry blossoms scatter, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I love cherry blossoms, but I don't like watching them scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to pay any attention to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's sad watching something beautiful scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's why I don't really like flower gazing that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I can understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but I think maybe the beauty of flowers strike people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}because they blossom so brilliantly, then scatter just as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't that yawn just now good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were still doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! Those men left because you just had to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My mistake, my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be funny. Guess it was pretty far off the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attitude really hasn't changed since our college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who cares if those silly guys don't like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling silly guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you actually liked them quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is that it, Nyamo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to catch a guy that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be wrong if I did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? Well, so very, very sorry then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Let's go drink another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's see, the pen name is Rice Cake With Bean Jam Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's an awfully sweet sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, Rice Cake With Bean Jam Chocolate has requested
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yu Asakawa's "My Heart Is That Of A Little Girl and I Parachute"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, I love this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagura was saying something about us having freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that was supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think she meant that, be it club activities or studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're working really hard at it, you sometimes get frantic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether you'll be able to accomplish your goals or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that we're working really hard at. She probably meant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we have more freedom because we have nothing to be frantic about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.19,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.25\b1\fs63\frz313.226\c&HA6BA8C&\pos(301.348,526.5)\3c&H788467&}Miracle Diet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, personally, I actually kind of envy the people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,who have something they can get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I join any clubs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying at this late date?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.59,EpisodeTitle,,131,0,0,,{\fad(277,0)}Cherry Blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You run at school and run at night as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was having a hard time falling asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was running because I wanted to feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But after looking at these cherry blossoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to think I'll be able to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I'm doing because I want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet I get stressed over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you get to go to the Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, you see, Satchin from Saitama Prefecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}being dumped is certainly a sad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but you're not the only one in pain when your feelings aren't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's right. Take Nakku. He's been dumped countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've been dumped left and right by girls since I was in school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and I ended up with the nickname, Emperor of Being Dumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, look at what you made me say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So cheer up, Satchin. We're cheering for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why anyone would send postcards to a show like this, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The pen name on the next postcard is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh! Little Tearful Diet Girl! Oh, I remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the girl who's been trying all sorts of dieting methods, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Apparently, all she does is diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not nice to laugh at her, Nakku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's a huge problem for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right, right, I shouldn't be laughing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's see, "Nakku, Mitchy, please listen to this."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"This time, I tried the grainless diet."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow, the grainless diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The grainless diet's the one you tried last month and failed at!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"This is where you don't eat any rice, bread, or noodles."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Instead, you eat fruits, vegetables, and oily things."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"It's a very revolutionary method of dieting."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's a bull's-eye, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I read about it in a magazine article and immediately tried it."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Unlike previous diets, there was no hunger to deal with,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You send postcards to shows like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"So I felt I could keep it up."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I thought I'd be extremely lucky if I could lose weight this way,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Yomi! This is just embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"But having run out of ideas in her repertoire,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Tearful Diet Girl, was it?! Oh, so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"My mother made curry and rice for dinner."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Having rice for the first time in three days, it was just delicious."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"It was so delicious, I ended up having seconds!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's see, "The next day, when I weighed myself,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"{\an8}I weighed more than I had three days ago!" Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"{\an8}The enemy of the grainless diet was my mother's menu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I intend to keep at it and go on to trying another diet. " That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sent it in so people would laugh, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It pisses me off when you're laughing right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eating curry without rice definitely sounds pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry to hear that, Little Tearful Diet Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let us know again when you've tried another diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll be rooting for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, let's move on to the next postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're responding to the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Little Tearful Diet Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with it, but it's too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko really seemed like she had her stuff together, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The men that Eiko brought along...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they thought we were rather childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think maybe I'll try looking into an arranged marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An arranged marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some talk of that sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to, why don't you? It's your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It is my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that spring makes you so sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you stay up late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Osaka! Get it together! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent! A magnificent yawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.41,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}kokoro ni hane wo motte\NWith wings upon your soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:15.39,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}tsutaete mune no sasayaki\NConvey the whispers of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:19.08,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}ima, kaze ni notte\NNow, riding the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:26.88,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}kokoro wa hoshi no kanata (hoshi no kanata)\NYour soul is beyond the stars (beyond the stars).
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:30.05,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}negai wa kanarazu kanau\NYour wishes will come true, without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:38.75,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}ai ni kite sono kagi wa mirai he\NCome see me, that key is for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:44.03,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}mado ni sotto yobu koe wa\NThe voice calling softly by the window
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.67,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}koi no yokan soshite\NSpeaks of love to come and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:52.05,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}mada touku no ai de mo\NEven if the love is still far off,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:56.43,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}shinjiteru asu wo shinjiteru kimi wo\NI have faith in tomorrow, I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:58.22,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Raspberry heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:03.91,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}hitori ja naitte yakusoku shita ne heaven\NI promised you that you're not alone, remember, heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:08.76,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Raspberry Heaven amai namida\NRaspberry heaven... such sweet tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.11,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}rakuen de mata hohoende ne\NSmile again in paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:15.15,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Raspberry heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:20.74,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}mukae ni kita yasashii yume no heaven\NI've come for you, the heaven of gentle dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:25.62,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Raspberry heaven, I'm coming back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:30.19,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}rakuen no hana saita hi ni\NOn the day the flowers in paradise bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:32.22,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}kimi to futari...\NYou and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:36.86,AzumangaED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}futari de aimashou\NLet's meet, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:42.41,Bubble,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112.36,216)}Next
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:42.41,Bubble,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114.382,434.25)}Azumanga\NDaioh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After all's said and done,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess those guys are already third year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling Chiyo-chan's grown quite a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! Time flows equally for all people. Ain't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, my students gave me a present for my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurosawa, what did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A present...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Presents?! Who cares about birthdays?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna age that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand, but things will continue next week.
